         I have a 60 enchatner and a 58 necro.  Let me tell you that Demi Lich makes KEI seem so slow.  Yes, you have hp loss to worry about, but with regen3, Z-heart, Belt of great turtle, my hps don't go down too fast.  </P><P>We do damage and heal ourself at the same time.  If you are just comparing a necro and an enchanter medding at the zone in from oom to full, then you are not comparing the classes the right way.  We have tremendous mana regen and are able to heal AND do damage with our spells.  Also, ToN isn't the best for hp replacement.  Always use vexing when you can, its much more efficent.  You ae not only healing yourself for 1100, but doing that much damage too.  </P><P>Even when I just demi lich and vex an eye(love my beads), my mana regen is FAR superior to rotten KEI.  Get KEI and then after you click it off and go back to lich you can tell me how great KEI is.</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
